<div class="about-section">
    <div class="about-section-header">
        <div class="about-icon">🔬</div>
        <h2>Project Overview</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="about-content">
        <p>The GLPF Microplastic Project is a collaborative research initiative focused on understanding and addressing microplastic pollution in the Great Lakes ecosystem. Our data collection system enables researchers, environmental organizations, and citizen scientists to contribute to a comprehensive database of microplastic observations.</p>
        
        <div class="about-highlights">
            <div class="highlight-card">
                <div class="highlight-icon">📊</div>
                <h3>Data Collection</h3>
                <p>Gathering microplastic observations across the Great Lakes region through standardized protocols</p>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight-card">
                <div class="highlight-icon">🔍</div>
                <h3>Research</h3>
                <p>Analyzing patterns and impacts of microplastic pollution to inform environmental policy</p>
            </div>            <div class="highlight-card">
                <div class="highlight-icon">🌊</div>
                <h3>Conservation</h3>
                <p>Developing strategies to reduce microplastic contamination in our freshwater ecosystems</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

